OL,3,CCommunity 'absolutely thrilled' after
OL,4,Cstolen altar cross returned 30 years on
OL,6,FAn altar cross that was stolen from a
OL,7,Fchurch in Gloucestershire in 1994- has
OL,8,Fbeen returned.
OL,10,FThe silver ornament was taken from All
OL,11,FSaints' Church in North Cerney 30
OL,12,Fyears ago and the church community
OL,13,Fpresumed they'd never see it again.
OL,15,FBut in an unexpected turn of events,
OL,16,Fat the end of October this year, it
OL,17,Fwas left on the doorstep of retired
OL,18,Fverger Elmore Crump.
