OL,3,CCommunity 'absolutely thrilled' after
OL,4,Cstolen altar cross returned 30 years on
OL,6,FThe silver cross was "tarnished black"
OL,7,Fand was left with a note reading:
OL,8,F"You'll know where this belongs."
OL,10,FMark Tufnell, the church warden, said
OL,11,Fthe cross was stolen as part of a
OL,12,Fspate of thefts in the area at the
OL,13,Ftime.
OL,15,FHe told ITV News West Country: "There
OL,16,Fwas a break in to the local pub, which
OL,17,Fis the Bathurst Arms.
