OL,3,CCommunity 'absolutely thrilled' after
OL,4,Cstolen altar cross returned 30 years on
OL,6,F"There was a break in at the old
OL,7,Frectory, which is next door to the
OL,8,Fchurch, and fuel was taken from the
OL,9,Fcars.
OL,11,F"Then into the church itself, a plank
OL,12,Fwas placed so that a small child was
OL,13,Fable to climb into the sacristy
OL,14,Fthrough the outside window.
OL,16,F"And the only thing that they were
OL,17,Fable to take that wasn't locked away
OL,18,Fwas this silver cross. We thought we'd
OL,19,Fnever see it again."
