OL,3,CCommunity 'absolutely thrilled' after
OL,4,Cstolen altar cross returned 30 years on
OL,6,FThe cross had been given to the church
OL,7,Fby Lady Winfred Murray. Her son, Alex
OL,8,FMurray, was "absolutely thrilled" to
OL,9,Fhear it had been returned.
OL,11,FMark said he believes a guilty
OL,12,Fconscience may have caught up with the
OL,13,Fthieves.
OL,15,FHe added: "I don't know why the cross
OL,16,Fwasn't sold or passed on.
OL,18,F"Maybe they kept it. Maybe they found
OL,19,Fit too difficult to pass on and then
OL,20,Fas time's gone by.
