OL,3,CCommunity 'absolutely thrilled' after
OL,4,Cstolen altar cross returned 30 years on
OL,6,FHe said: "It's a silver plate, and it
OL,7,Fhas mother of pearl inlaid into it.
OL,9,F"And with two or three days of hard
OL,10,Fcleaning by Elmore, he's managed to
OL,11,Frestore it, and it now looks... I
OL,12,Fwould say better than it's ever
OL,13,Flooked, it's just been cleaned and I
OL,14,Fthink that's the beauty of silver, the
OL,15,Fbase metal that once it's cleaned, and
OL,16,Fwe can keep it cleaned.
OL,18,F"It looks tremendous. Mother of pearl
OL,19,Flooks wonderful.
