OL,3,CCommunity 'absolutely thrilled' after
OL,4,Cstolen altar cross returned 30 years on
OL,6,F"But somehow the silver plate and the
OL,7,Fmother of pearl sets it off
OL,8,Fparticularly well. It's the
OL,9,Fsimplicity, I think of the church.
OL,11,F"And it represents the simplicity of
OL,12,Fthe community that we celebrate in our
OL,13,Fparish."
